⚡ Physics

These functions handle physics-based movement.

move.accelerate() / move.decelerate()

move.accelerate(player, 0.6, 0, 8, 0);
move.decelerate(player, 0.4, 0);

Enter fullscreen mode

Exit fullscreen mode

